data.description: Best value anywhere and Wonderful Opportunity to Live in the Heart of Buckhead near the History Center and The Governors Mansion on Five beautifully landscaped acres! Adorable updated TWO BEDROOM,TWO BATH in quiet location with view of Garden and Pool area! Granite Kitchen counters and pass through to Dining area Stainless appliances and fridge included.. Mid Century Parquet hardwood floors throughout with new ceramic/laminate in kitchen. Brand new windows summer 2023! ALL UTILITES, CABLE, Electric, Gas, Water, Sewer, Pest control, property manager and POOL INCLUDED IN MONTHLY FEE. Garage is walk in level with side of building. Enjoy short walk to upscale Buckhead restaurants and shopping! There is No rental, No Pets, No FHA permitted at Slaton. There is an on site manager and on site storage is available. Meeting room with full kitchen is gratis to homeowners. Walk to restaurants and shopping! Best value in Buckhead! This delightful two bedroom is priced to sell today!  Slaton is a no smoking building with NO FHA financing, No Pets and No Rental NO exceptions.
